RIYADH: Saudi Arabia’s chief of staff, Gen. Fayyad bin Hamed Al-Ruwaili, met with the UK Defense Senior Adviser to the Middle East and North Africa, Air Marshal Martin Sampson, the Kingdom’s defense ministry said on Thursday.
During the meeting, they discussed bilateral relations and defense cooperation between the two countries, as well as the latest regional developments.
